# PCMPlayer

A simple PCM audio player designed for quick audio data preview.

## Features

- Supports PCM16 format audio playback
- Direct base64 encoded audio data input
- Clean and simple user interface

## Use Cases

This tool helps you verify audio data during development by:

- Quick playback of PCM audio data
- Audio format validation
- Content verification

## How to Use

1. Copy base64 encoded audio data into the input area
2. Click the play button to listen
